name: GENERATIVE ABSTRACT/ 🟦🟧 BLUE-GOLD Brushed (Special Edition)
description:
Generative artwork exploring colors and the emergent effect of stacking simple shapes, random colors glyphs scattered amongst an eternal sea of shades of colors representing the steps on the road to understanding.
All artworks are created using custom algorithms in processing. After the process of making images, these images have been turned into text coding art with artificial intelligence.
